The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Lanka crawl   to 84/3 
                                                                                                                       7                                      Lanka crawl   to 84/3 
                            
	Colombo: Sri Lanka, batting first on a new pitch, struggled for runs on a restricted opening day of the second Test against the West Indies, to crawl to 84 for three at the close on Tuesday. Bad light and rain curtailed play after only eight balls in the final session.           (REUTERS)                                                                                                                 
